  - q: "How are the five elements used in martial arts?"
    a: "Xingyiquan directly maps its five core fist techniques to the five elements: Pi (Metal/splitting), Zuan (Water/drilling), Beng (Wood/crushing), Pao (Fire/pounding), and Heng (Earth/crossing). The generating and overcoming cycles inform combat strategy and technique selection."
